name: VOXELFINE #9: "Girl with a Pearl Earring" by Johannes Vermeer 3D voxelart model (.glb)
description: I did a bad thing and made two Dutch pieces in a row. I made this one because, on the day I decided to make it, I saw the Vermeer painting several times. I figured I'd have to get to it eventually, and here it is. Proportions were the hardest part. Voxelfines are collectible 3D voxel models of iconic works of art. They are ready to be imported into a VR or AR experience of your choice. By Lorem Ipsum, 2021.
